Movie Recommendation System :
---------------------------
Many famous systems like Netflix, Prime etc use Movie recommendation systems.
link: https://github.com/TruptiAgrawal/MovieRecommendationSystem

Types:
------
1. content based - based on the content the user have watched before. 
2. populairty based - based on the frequency of series/movies watched by the users 
3. collaborative based - groups people based on same content such that when a new user joins in they get the similar content, users behavior and prefrence content

workflow of the project:
----------------------
1. Data - movie name, director, genre, description 
2. Data pre processing - cleaning
3. feature extraction - raw data into meaning full features (numerical) 
4. user input -> name of their fav movie, based on that suggest movies 
5. similarity confidence score - cosine similarity algorithm 
6. suggest list of movies 

